des: FUBU RADIO was launched on December 24th, 2015 by Keith Perrin Jr, Co-owner and founder of FUBU and Demetrius L. Brown. The station format is Hip Hop and R&B hits of today and yesterday. FUBU RADIO is entertaining, empowering, and connecting generations with content, music, and voices of people whose mission is to help other people be successful. FUBU RADIO is not just another radio station, we are a movement. Download the FUBU RADIO APP and Tap INTO THE MOVEMENT TODAY.
